>InputSignalWithTransform</a></code> 表示帶有 \n<code>transform</code> 函式的指令/元件輸入的特殊 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a></code>。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section><section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputSignalWithTransform</a>&lt;ReadT, WriteT&gt; extends <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&lt;ReadT&gt; {\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  <div class=\"descendants interface\">\n    <h2 id=\"子介面\">子介面<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#子介面\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <code><a href=\"api/core/InputSignal\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputSignal</a></code>\n    \n  </li>\n</ul>\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/core/InputSignal\"><code>InputSignal</code></a>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1t48aihkrnom6ehlq7zrxngg3\">獲取更多訊息。</p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1e6ua9hahx4y5adiepfzng6u6\">使用轉換的輸入訊號會捕獲一個額外的泛型用於其轉換寫入型別。轉換可以擴充套件輸入的接受繫結值，同時確保訊號輸入的值檢索仍然對應泛型輸入型別。</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nclass MyDir {\n  disabled = input(false, {\n    transform: (v: string|boolean) =&gt; convertToBoolean(v),\n  }); // <a href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputSignalWithTransform</a>&lt;boolean, string|boolean&gt;\n\n  click() {\n    this.disabled() // always returns a `boolean`.\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n  \n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/InputFunction\n - api/core/InputSignal\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/InputSignal\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#description\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#inputsignalwithtransform\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#see-also\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#子介面\n - api/core/Signal\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/authoring/input/input_signal.ts#L55-L84\n-->"}